summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 62E, page 152, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Homecroft Addition, South 64.6 ft. of west 120 ft. of Lot 5, Block 24, south 98.8 ft. of east 120 ft. of Lot 6, Block 25, located two lots north of West Graham St. on both sides of Delridge Way, as Neighborhood Business (BN) Zone.
